{"tid":2134163,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)雨傘學院 第1-2季","createTime":"2020-07-31T13:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T13:44:03.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd725b3482c25d705a9096ec582667f92badfd0","tid":2134163,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:29:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=889ba005\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=1ea4ed9c\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=739ff601\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://post76.hk/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/cambrdige-audio-edge-w-edge-nq0051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost76.hk%2Fnews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2Fcambrdige-audio-edge-w-edge-nq0051.jpg&h=5ac97ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1989年的一天，突然降生了四十三名嬰兒，他們的母親之間毫無關聯，而且在之前一天沒有任何懷孕的跡象。其中七名嬰兒由億萬富翁實業家雷吉納爾德&middot;哈格里維斯爵士領養，爵士創建了雨傘學院，為「孩子們」做好拯救世界的準備。但事情並沒有按計劃進行，在孩子們十幾歲的時候，這個家庭破裂了，整個團隊解散。當前，六名子女在獲悉爵士神秘死亡之後重聚，路德、迪亞哥、艾莉森、克勞斯、凡妮亞和「五號」一起解開養父死亡之謎。但由於他們的個性和能力各不相同，這個重組家庭再次面臨分崩離析，另外還有即將來臨的世界末日&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=6d4aed09\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=db7397b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee64164b3babc9a3657b8642216661db32ff7f6","tid":2134163,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baaf669c0c3adb92f5de3ebd891c3733d3f8019f","tid":2134163,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8198b6c2165a617fdaa9b0e3b566ce005e24afc6","tid":2134163,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score